    "description": "<p>ARROWCREST TECHNOLOGIES PTE LTD</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>ARROW</strong> - Focus, Sharpness and Precision in our Products, Decision Making and Directions<br>\n<strong>CREST</strong> - At the edge of modern technology, watching over the security of lives and properties&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>About ARROWCREST:-</strong><br>\nArrowcrest Technologies Pte Ltd is a leading System Design and Integration House for Intelligence Security Systems, founded in March 1998.<br>\n<br>\nWe provide customary development of integrated security management suite to satisfy the ever-changing demand of intelligence system.<br>\n<br>\nWe gained significant market application of our product with major customers across government offices, finance sector, statutory organizations, and emerging SMEs etc, in Singapore, Maldives, Malaysia, Indonesia, Vietnam and Brunei. <u>Company Vision</u>:-<br>\nTo withstand our leading position in the realm of surveillance and niche in the world of ever-changing technology.<br>\n<br>\n<u>Company Mission</u>:-<br>\nTo seek continuous breakthrough providing solutions to the daily sophisticated security needs.<br>\n<br>\n<u>Company Values</u>:-<br>\nVersatile application of security device and technology, not restricted by brand or any shortfall, incorporating the gist of each and striking the best balancing point of technology and price combination in achieving the best solution designed for each individual integrated security demand.</p>",
